want to know more about me?

Jemma Mae (they/she) is a graphic designer and content creator in Spokane, Washington. They specialize in branding, art direction and social media content creation and design. Jemma has additional experience in photography, videography, logo design and sound design.

Jemma is a social media influencer with over 100,000 followers across their YouTube, Instagram and TikTok platforms with a focus on beauty, fashion and lifestyle content.

Jemma is a model with experience in commercial and runway, a Harajuku fashion enthusiast and expert in all things cute.
